<body>
    <h1>Email Validation Form</h1>
    <p>This form provides real-time feedback on email input using a simple regex. Type an email to see the border change color.</p>

    <form id="emailForm">
        <label for="email">Enter your email:</label>
        <input type="email" id="email" class="email-input" placeholder="e.g., user@example.com">
